data.description: Great 2 story, 2 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath condo in Hampton Ridge with open floor plan.   Desirable private entrance on back side of building and prime location viewing grassy area and berm.  Open concept great room, dining and kitchen.  9' 1st floor ceilings.  Living room features large windows, bay window and open to dining.  Large kitchen features updated counters, eating bar plus a walk-in pantry off adjoining laundry room. Laminate flooring throughout 1st floor.   Primary bedroom with vaulted ceiling and huge walk-in closet.  Some updates include vanity/lighting/laminate flooring in primary bath, kitchen counters furnace 2/15/24.  1 car attached garage off laundry/mud room.  Dues also include water/sewer.   Complex includes community pool and clubhouse, playground and walking paths.  Great location with easy access to shopping, restaurants, downtown and highway.
